(7, 1, '2014-04-07 10:51:54', '2014-04-07 10:51:54', 'Acorn is an independent alternative asset manager serving the investment needs of a select group of sophisticated investors by providing a platform for those investors to directly participate in private equity. This platform consists of LLP funds and an investment holding company in which investments are housed.\r\n\r\nIn addition, Acorn also provides investment advice in corporate transactions.', 'Overview', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'business-overview', '', '', '2014-05-06 13:54:43', '2014-05-06 11:54:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/~tyronestafford/acorn/?page_id=7', 0, 'page', '', 0),
