(13, 1, '2014-04-07 10:52:47', '2014-04-07 10:52:47', '<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">A well-known South African institutional investor invests R78 million in Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted April 2, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn releases a flash update on performance and transactions for the start of 2014 to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted February 10, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn completes the purchase of a significant stake in Overberg Agri through the newly incorporated Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd in a deal worth approximately R200m.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted February 7, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted January 31, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn completes second exit from General Fund 1. USC is sold to a trade player.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted January 20, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn completes first exit from General Fund 1. Target Investment is sold to a trade player.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted January 13, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted October 31, 2013 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted July 31, 2013 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted April 30, 2013 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted January 31, 2013 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn successfully concluded a transaction between Overberg Agri and Moorreesburgse Koringboere to the value of R927 million.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted November 27, 2012 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted October 31, 2012 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted July 31, 2012 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted April 30, 2012 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted January 31, 2012 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted October 31, 2011 by the Investment Team</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn General Fund One is fully invested. This is an achievement the Acorn team is proud of as it was achieved within 21 months of the fund´s first close.</a></h3>\r\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted August 26, 2011 by the Investment Team</p>', 'News', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'news', '', '', '2014-05-14 16:31:06', '2014-05-14 14:31:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost/~tyronestafford/acorn/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
