r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Acorn can add the most value in SMEs and we see the impact of our involvement on the bottom line and the communities in which our investee companies operate.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'SME', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '42-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-10 12:26:13', '2014-04-10 12:26:13', '', 42, 'http://192.168.1.15/~tyronestafford/acorn/42-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
