(110, 1, '2014-04-10 12:46:38', '2014-04-10 12:46:38', 'Acorn is in the on-going process of developing an ESG Scorecard for every investee company. This process involves meeting with management at each company to discuss and identify the environmental, social and governance risks applicable to that company. Once the risks have been identified a plan is formulated to address those risks and a measure of success decided upon. Information is relayed back to Acorn on a quarterly basis prior to meetings with management and the issues are once again discussed at the meetings as part of a continuous risk identification and improvement process. This scorecard is sent to investors as part of the quarterly performance updates.', 'Scorecard', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '84-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-10 12:46:38', '2014-04-10 12:46:38', '', 84, 'http://192.168.1.15/~tyronestafford/acorn/84-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
