(112, 1, '2014-05-12 13:28:27', '2014-05-12 11:28:27', '<h2><a style="color: #698c00;">A well-known South African institutional investor invests R78 million in Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd.</a></h2>\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted April 2, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn releases a flash update on performance and transactions for the start of 2014 to investors and interested parties.</a></h2>\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted February 10, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn completes the purchase of a significant stake in Overberg Agri through the newly incorporated Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd in a deal worth approximately R200m.</a></h2>\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted February 7, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h2>\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted January 31, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn completes second exit from General Fund 1. USC is sold to a trade player.</a></h2>\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted January 20, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><a style="color: #698c00;">Acorn completes first exit from General Fund 1. Target Investment is sold to a trade player.</a></h2>\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted January 13, 2014 by the Investment Team</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><a style="color: #698c00;">The quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.</a></h2>\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted October 31, 2013 by the Investment Team</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><a style="color: #